1.plot: Reairing of RJ's always been disappointed in himself for not vlogging while building up and running his previous company, RJTIO before he moved on from it. So, he decided as he builds up his new startup, Pearit, he wouldn't stop with an office tour. Today he takes you along for the ride; from waking up with him in LA and into work, all the way to an engagement party at night - Can't say it didn't happen.

imdb.plot outline: Raw, unconventional, wild stories from people preserving through the daily grind while trying to achieve some kind of success. They may not know what they want to do yet, or even who they are, or who they want to become exactly - but they are all connected in their belief to want to do something with their lives. Inspiration, drama, love, fun, and more are intertwined throughout episodes that don't always follow a specific person, storyline, or character in a linear fashion.
